race.comment: GOOD LUCK BABE (3) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at this track but was a Grade 5 winner two back at this track. Will find this more suitable and can atone. IS IT ME (2) comes off an average effort last start when fifth at Hobart over 340m behind Ducati Roy (20.15) in a Grade 5. One of the better hopes. UNCONVICTED (5) has missed the frame the last couple but was a Grade 5 winner three back (26.21) at Hobart over 461m. Expecting sharp improvement. BUCKLE UP RAE (8) collected a minor prize last start and must be considered.
